_:Na4af86fc8b1d4d4d8945d5e7cdb16d29 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Georgia Gould was appointed Minister of State (Minister for School Standards) at the Department for Education on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Parliamentary Secretary at the Cabinet Office between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Georgia was elected as the MP for Queen’s Park and Maida Vale in July 2024.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
